summary: A collection of eight CME saves for ECE.
descriptionHtml:
[color=gray] Some people have trouble making characters or faces, and some people find themselves bored with their characters. I figured I'd toss this out here for those people. The looks of each preset will change with whatever hair, face textures, or other cosmetic mods you have installed.
___________ _____ _____ ___ ___ __ _


[size=5]Eight CME Character slots for Enhanced Character Edit (ECE). One character slot per non-beast race is included. Female only.[/size]

____________ ____ ____ ___ ____ __ _

These saves go in your Documents > my games > skyrim > CME_save folder, so make sure to backup any existing saves you have stored in that folder.[/color]
[color=white]Enhanced Character Edit is required and Racemenu will not work as a substitute unless it loads CME saves.[/color]
author: Wyn Xombii
